name: PAIR OF LEGS
description:
"PAIR OF LEGS"

foto ini saya ambil saat saya sedang hunting foto Human interest di jogja tepatnya di Malioboro, saat saya sedang melihat ke arah bawah tak sengaja saya melihat objek yang sangat menarik dimana ada 2 pasang kaki yang sedang melangkah bersamaan

I took this photo when I was hunting for Human Interest photos in Jogja, precisely in Malioboro, when I was looking down I accidentally saw a very interesting object where there were 2 pairs of legs walking together
